OL,3,CMan admits killing elderly church
OL,4,Cwarden during burglary
OL,6,FA 36-year-old man has admitted killing
OL,7,Fan elderly church warden at her home.
OL,9,FDavid Parish, of Halyard Drive,
OL,10,FBridgwater, pleaded guilty to the
OL,11,Fmanslaughter of Beryl Purdy by reason
OL,12,Fof diminished responsibility.
OL,14,FParish also pleaded not guilty to
OL,15,Fmurder during a hearing at Bristol
OL,16,FCrown Court.
