OL,6,FThe prosecutor, Anna Vigars KC, said:
OL,7,F"We have received psychiatric reports
OL,8,Fcommissioned by the defence and the
OL,9,FCrown. They both come to the same
OL,10,Fconclusion.
OL,12,F"I can confirm that, were a plea of
OL,13,Fnot guilty to murder but guilty to
OL,14,Fmanslaughter by reason of diminished
OL,15,Fresponsibility to be entered, that
OL,16,Fwould be acceptable to the Crown."
OL,18,FPolice were called to reports of a
OL,19,Fburglary at Mrs Purdy's home at about
OL,20,F5.45pm on March 27 last year in
OL,21,FBroomfield, near Bridgwater.
