OL,3,CMan admits killing elderly church
OL,4,Cwarden during burglary
OL,6,FShe was found seriously injured and
OL,7,Fdied at her home.
OL,9,FIn a statement, Mrs Purdy's family
OL,10,Fsaid: "As a family, we are devastated
OL,11,Fto have lost a dearly loved wife,
OL,12,Fmother and granny.
OL,14,F"Bez was a caring person who would
OL,15,Fhelp anyone in need and was very much
OL,16,Fpart of the village, being a church
OL,17,Fwarden for 20 years.
OL,19,F"We will miss her very much and we are
OL,20,Fall struggling to understand why this
OL,21,Fhappened to such a lovely person."
